data.description:
Welcome to this immaculate move-in ready home in Laveen Meadows on a premium lot with no neighbors behind! This home has a well-thought-out floorplan featuring 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a spacious greatroom. The kitchen has beautiful upgrades featuring granite countertops, maple crown molded cabinets, stainless steel gas appliances, and a kitchen island with a breakfast bar. The great room offers neutral tile floors and a ceiling fan. The stairs are stunning with wrought iron finishes. The primary suite is upstairs and generous in size with a delightful ensuite bathroom featuring dual sink vanity, separate shower and tub, and a huge walk-in closet! The backyard is immaculate with an extended covered patio finished with a ceiling fan, a paved patio extension, easy-care artificial grass, and a stunning view of the community green belt. This home is a dream! 

Laveen Meadows is in a prime Laveen location close to the freeway, shopping, dining, and the new movie theatre being built! Do not miss out on this home!
